{"word":"G3828 - Παμφυλία - Pamphylía - pam-fool-ee'-ah - Pamphylia","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">Παμφυλία</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">Pamphylía</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">pam-fool-ee'-ah</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Pamphylia</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Noun Location / இடப்பெயர்</span>"},{"paragraph":"பம்பிலியா - ஓர் இடத்தின் பெயர்"},{"paragraph":"Pamphylia"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From a compound of <a href=\"#/G3956 - πᾶς - pâs - pas/3956\">G3956</a> and <a href=\"#/G5443 - φυλή - phylḗ - foo-lay'/5443\">G5443</a>; <i>every tribal</i>, that is, <i>heterogeneous</i> (<a href=\"#/G5561 - χώρα - chṓra - kho'-rah/5561\">G5561</a> being implied); <i>Pamphylia</i>, a region of Asia Minor: - Pamphylia.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}